text: Georcy-Stéphanie Thiffeault Picard is an archer from Canada. Picard competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics. She was born on 8 February 1991.Georcy Thiffeault Picard == References == Category:Canadian archers Category:Olympians for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Montreal Category:Living people Category:1991 births
